### 1. Add New Prospect
POST http://localhost:3000/api/prospect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "AgentId": "7b407c2d-3145-40b0-8c47-1d6f62351b2c",
  "FirstName": "John",
  "Surname": "Mwangi",
  "LastName": "Doe",
  "PhoneNumber": "0712345678",
  "Email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "Notes": "Interested in motor insurance, current policy expires in 2 months"
}

### 2. Add External Policy to Prospect
POST http://localhost:3000/api/prospect/policy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ProspectId": "a5400e8a-bb0d-4fba-b153-81841bfc56b5",
  "CompanyName": "AAR Insurance",
  "PolicyNumber": "POL-2024-001234",
  "PolicyType": "Motor Insurance",
  "ExpiryDate": "2025-03-15",
  "Notes": "Current comprehensive motor policy, expires soon"
}

### 3. Update Prospect
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/prospect/prospect-uuid-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "FirstName": "John",
  "Surname": "Mwangi",
  "LastName": "Doe",
  "PhoneNumber": "0712345679",
  "Email": "john.doe.updated@example.com",
  "Notes": "Updated contact information - interested in multiple policies"
}

### 4. Delete Prospect
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/prospect/prospect-uuid-here

### 5. Convert Prospect to Client
POST http://localhost:3000/api/prospect/prospect-uuid-here/convert-to-client
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Address": "123 Kimathi Street, Nairobi",
  "NationalId": "12345678",
  "DateOfBirth": "1985-06-15"
}

### 6. Get Agent Prospects
GET http://localhost:3000/api/agent/7b407c2d-3145-40b0-8c47-1d6f62351b2c/prospects

### 7. Get Prospect Policies
GET http://localhost:3000/api/prospect/prospect-uuid-here/policies

### 8. Get Prospect Statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/agent/7b407c2d-3145-40b0-8c47-1d6f62351b2c/prospect-statistics

### 9. Get Expiring Prospect Policies (Default 30 days)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/agent/7b407c2d-3145-40b0-8c47-1d6f62351b2c/expiring-prospect-policies

### 10. Get Expiring Prospect Policies (Custom days ahead)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/agent/7b407c2d-3145-40b0-8c47-1d6f62351b2c/expiring-prospect-policies?daysAhead=60

### 11. Auto-Create Reminders for Expiring Prospect Policies
POST http://localhost:3000/api/agent/7b407c2d-3145-40b0-8c47-1d6f62351b2c/prospect-reminders/auto-create
Content-Type: application/json

